article_title: In glare of spotlight, Kentucky's Obamacare program is ready, experts say
article_text: After years of chatter and debate, some 640,000uninsuredKentuckians on Tuesday will have their first full look at what the Affordable Care Act — or as it's commonly called, Obamacare — means to them.
